t: "Ask ňĻthem, O Prophetňļ, ‚ÄúCan any of your associate-gods guide to the truth?‚ÄĚ Say, ‚ÄúňĻOnlyňļ Allah guides to the truth.‚ÄĚ Who then is more worthy to be followed: the One Who guides to the truth or those who cannot find the way unless guided? What is the matter with you? How do you judge"